welcome to the macdonald research group web site. the picture to the left is an example
of the type of high aspect ratio, single crytstal silicon, movable structures members of
the macdonald group are fabricating.  this web site will introduce you to the members of
the group and their work as well as our processing techniques and applications thereof.


